Registration Page
- Create a new form to register new users
- Validate inputs (e.g., username, password).
- Store registered users in localStorage.

Login
- Implement a login form.
- Authenticate users against stored credentials in localStorage.

Home Page (Guarded Route)
- Design the main dashboard where tasks will be displayed.
- Implement guarded route using react-router-dom to ensure only authenticated users can access this page.
- Display a welcome message or user-specific information.

Task Management
- Task List Component:

- - Create a component to display a list of tasks.
- - Fetch tasks from localStorage on component mount.
- - Allow filtering tasks by priority (High, Medium, Low) and status (Incomplete, Complete).

- Add Task Form:

- - Implement a form to add new tasks.
- - Include fields for task name, description, priority, due date (optional).


- Update and Delete Tasks:

- - Enable editing of task details (name, description, priority, due date).
- - Allow users to mark tasks as completed or delete tasks completely.

- Profile Page
- - Create a page where users can view and update their profile details.
- - Include fields for username, password (with validation), and any other relevant user information.

Design
- Ensure the app has a user-friendly interface with intuitive navigation.
- Use appropriate colors, typography, and layout to enhance usability.
- Implement interactivity cues (e.g., hover effects, clickable elements).

Notifications and Error Handling
- Provide notifications for successful operations (e.g., task added, updated, deleted).
- Display appropriate error messages for failed operations (e.g., incorrect login details).

Responsive Design
- Ensure the app is responsive across different devices and screen sizes.
- Test responsiveness at common breakpoints (320px, 480px, 768px, 1024px, 1200px).

Data Persistence
- Utilize localStorage for data storage and retrieval (tasks, user information).
- Implement CRUD operations ensuring data integrity and persistence.

Bonus Features (Optional, Post-submission)
-   Implement additional features like overdue task warnings, task completion tracking, and a separate page for completed tasks.